                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote>
                                <p>Each of the two upper corners has a protruding ram's head with a
                                    ribbon coming down from each one's horn, connected by a floral
                                    garland. Between the two is a phiale relief. At the bottom two
                                    corners, there are two carved sphinxes, and a waterfowl is
                                    between the two.</p>
