            <div type="translation">
                <p>Of Publius Fundanius Velinus, son of Publius, from the Teretina tribe.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The original altar, containing the text and more elaborate decoration, can be
                    found at the Louvre.</p>
